data.description: Stunning 2 year old home in the Edinburgh area of Chesapeake. Flex room with double glass doors that makes a great play room or office, followed by an open-concept designed kitchen, dining room & family room. Upstairs discover all four generously sized bedrooms and the laundry room. The master bedroom is a true sanctuary with two walk-in closets and ensuite bathroom featuring a double sink vanity with granite countertops and an oversized tiled walk-in shower with dual shower heads. This beautiful home features numerous upgrades, the chef's kitchen with upgraded appliances, a spacious island, and additional cabinet space. Customs built-ins throughout the home living spaces, the mudroom and pantry. Covered back patio creates an ideal retreat for enjoying the expansive backyard that the large corner lot provides, surrounded by a privacy white vinyl fence. Also in the backyard is a custom built shed. Go green and save money on utilities with a solar panel system.
